# Health and Society

## LOs
1. Components of health system science
2. Equality vs equity
3. Determinants of health
4. Impact of DoH on health outcomes

## Core Domains of Health Systems
- HC structures
- Policy, economics, management
- Health information technology (ex. EHR)
- Population/public health
- Value-based care (how do values and $value impact care?)
- Health systems improvement
- Leadership
- Evidence-based medicine
- Team-based medicine
- Ethics

## Definitions of Health
- Holistic wellbeing vs physical wellbeing
- Ability to adapt or self-manage

## Upsetting vs. Triggering
- Upsetting:
	- Normal reaction to hearing something that is discomforting
	- It is difficult but not happening to you
	- Able to acknowledge feelings in present
	- Regulable
- Triggered:
	- Re-experiencing by flashback or memories
	- Unable to separate experience from reality
	- Difficulty staying grounded
